<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>File Data Microservice</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>

	<h1 class="text-center">File Metadata Microservice</h1>
	<h3 class="text-center"> FreeCodeCamp Back-End API section</h3>
	

	<div class="container">
		<form role='form' action="/uploads" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
			<input type="file" name="file">
			<input class="btn btn-primary" type="submit" value="Upload">
		</form>
	</div>

	<div class="container" style="margin-top: 35px;">
		<h4>User Stories: </h4>

		<ul>
			<li>I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.</li>
			<li>When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response</li>
		</ul>

	</div>
	
</body>
</html>